Signature: answer_question

Input JSON:
{
  "question": "What changed?",
  "context": "A programs package was added."
}

Output JSON Schema:
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "answer": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": "concise answer"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "answer"
  ],
  "additionalProperties": false
}

Return only JSON matching the output schema.